	(20129, 11, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The timeways are currently ranked in order from least catastrophic to most catastrophic. Note that they are all classified as catastrophic, meaning that any single one of these timeways collapsing would mean that your world would end. We only classify them in such a way so that the heroes and adventurers that are sent here know which timeway best suits their abilities.'),
