	(3946, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Число моих сторонников уменьшается богиня, и моя собственная власть скоро будет недостаточна чтобы держать в повиновении демонов Фелвудского леса.'),
	(3946, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Богиня, дайте мне власть, чтобы победить моих врагов! Прошу вас услышьте!, пожалуйста. Я весь в отчаянии!'),
	(3946, 2, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Что... что это? Может это ответ на мои просьбы? Элуна дала мне это оружие, эту косу чтобы поразить демонов.'),
	(4509, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'In the throes of the Sundering, Ameth\'Aran was at the whim of the terror that gripped the land. There was little hope for survival.'),
	(4509, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Athrikus came to us. He told us that he could save us from harm. He cast a spell upon us to protect us from harm.'),
	(4509, 2, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When the shaking stopped, his true motives were revealed. We were trapped, and he was slowly draining our powers.'),
	(4509, 3, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'There were hundreds imprisoned by his spell. Now only a few remain in their prisons. He would speak to us sometimes.'),
	(4509, 4, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'He worried that his power weakened, that soon even we last of his precious soulgems would fade and die.'),
	(4509, 5, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'His lieutenant, Ilkrud Magthrull possesses a tome which might indicate the location of the remaining soulgems.'),
	(35476, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Of course I was the one chosen to summon a demon for the competitors. I am Wilfred Fizzlebang, master summoner! Demons quail before the mere thought of being under my will!'),
